{
  "texts": [
    "Huong and Phuc [25] introduced a framework for extracting triples (subject-predicate-object relationships) from Vietnamese.",
    "However, their technique has limitations in handling complex sentences and is applied to the travel area.",
    "KG-augmented LLMsOne major hurdle for LLMs is their occasional struggle with factual accuracy and hallucinations.",
    "This is where KGs come in.",
    "KGs offer a structured representation of knowledge, encoding entities and their relationships in a machine-readable format."
  ]
}